  "title": "Civil Resident Technical Officer",
  "description": "<p>Full time job<br />1. On-site in supervising and inspecting construction work to ensure that all works comply wish statutory and client requirements.<br />2. Work closely with C&S QP, and other Resident Technical Officers and contractors to resolve site issues and ensure timely project completion.<br />3. Implement and sustain the site supervision quality & safety assurance system.<br />4. Carry out supervision of structural & demolition works by identifying any non-conformity of contractor's on-site works.<br />5. Monitor project progress schedule and quality standards<br />6. Maintain and updated site records on project progress.<br />7. Ensure proper maintenance and updating of site documentation for ongoing works, site meetings, safety records, method, statements shop drawings, as-build submissions etc.<br />8. Be familiar with and check all method statement and drawings (including authority submission and shop drawings.)<br />9. Carry out regular site checks on contractors & ensure compliance with health and work safety per MOM regulations.<br /></p><p>Please email your CV to: pe@qp.sg</p>",
